    <div class="main-content">
        <h2>What is Hacktoberfest?</h2>
        <p>Hacktoberfest is a month-long celebration of open source software. During October, open source enthusiasts and developers from around the world come together to contribute to open source projects and earn rewards.</p>
        <h2>How to Participate</h2>
        <p>To participate in Hacktoberfest, you need to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Sign up on the <a href="https://hacktoberfest.digitalocean.com/">Hacktoberfest website</a></li>
            <li>Contribute to open source projects by submitting pull requests on GitHub</li>
            <li>Complete a minimum of 4 pull requests to earn a limited edition Hacktoberfest T-shirt</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Get Involved</h2>
        <p>Join the open source community and start contributing today!</p>
        <a class="cta-button" href="https://hacktoberfest.digitalocean.com/">Get Started</a>
    </div>
